summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 153 of the Official Land Use Map (Volume 14 of Plats, page 45, Records of King County) to rezone property located at 5640 16th Avenue Southwest, from Lowrise 1 (L1) to Lowrise 1 / Residential Commercial (L1 / RC) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Seattle Chinese Garden Society, C.F. 306768, Project Number 2400096)
